The '''big pocket gopher''' ('''''Orthogeomys lanius''''') is a species of [[rodent]] in the family [[Geomyidae]]. It is [[endemic]] to [[Mexico]], where it has only been found on the southeastern slopes of [[Pico de Orizaba|Mt. Orizaba]], at an elevation of 1300 m.<ref name=iucn/>  

